| Title           = However, That Room Continues to Portray An Endless Everyday Scene.
| AltTitle        = Saredo, Sono Heya wa Owara nu Nichijō o Enjitsuzukeru.
| RAltTitle       = &nbsp;({{Nihongo2|されど、その部屋は終わらぬ日常を演じ続ける。}})
| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2015|5|15}}<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150507182502/http://www.tbs.co.jp/tv/20150514_C033.html|archivedate=May 7, 2015|url=http://www.tbs.co.jp/tv/20150514_C033.html|title=やはり俺の青春ラブコメはまちがっている。続　♯７[字][デ] TBSテレビ|deadurl=yes|publisher=[[Tokyo Broadcasting System|Tokyo Broadcasting System Television, Inc]]|language=Japanese|accessdate=May 7, 2015}}</ref>
