==Home media==
[[Marvelous (company)|Marvelous!]] began releasing the series in Japan on seven [[Blu-ray]] and [[DVD]] volumes between June 24 and December 16, 2015.<ref name="BD Volumes"/> A few of the Limited Edition Blu-ray volumes will include bonus [[light novels]] of the series.

